### ROMs (never tracked — live on moon under assets/games/, .gitignored here).
### Leading slash scopes the pattern to the repo root so `pkg/games/` (the
### Go package that owns library scanning) isn't caught by it.
assets/games/
/games/

### Runtime data (lives on deployment target, never in git)
/cores/
/saves/
/libretro/
/dolphin/

# xemu AppImage extraction — staged by scripts/extract-xemu.sh for
# Dockerfile.run to COPY in. Regenerable; don't commit the ~100MB blob.
vendor/xemu/

### Secrets (IGDB OAuth, future API keys) — live on moon under
### ~/containers/cloudplay/secrets/ and are bind-mounted read-only into
### the worker. Never commit.
/secrets/
*.env

### BIOS / emulator artifacts kept locally as recovery material after
### we lost them once to a stray rsync --delete. Copyrighted, never
### published. Canonical backup lives on moon's NAS at
### /var/mnt/data/media/games/.backups/cloudplay/.
Xbox-Emulator-Files.zip
SCPH-*.bin
mcpx_*.bin
